OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777054266
OL,3,CMan who poured hot oil on wife jailed
OL,4,Cfor attempted murder
OL,6,FA Birmingham man who tried to murder
OL,7,Fhis wife by pouring hot oil on her
OL,8,Fhead has been jailed.
OL,10,FRaju Mollah, 50, and his wife had
OL,11,Fargued days before he stamped on her,
OL,12,Fkicked her and pushed a mop into her
OL,13,Fface on 12 January last year, the
OL,14,FCrown Prosecution Service (CPS) said.
OL,16,FMollah's wife, who was found by police
OL,17,Flying in a pool of oil, suffered
OL,18,Fsevere burns, a minor bleed to the
OL,19,Fbrain, missing teeth, wounds to her
OL,20,Fface and head, and singed hair.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
