PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777054266
OL,3,CMan who poured hot oil on wife jailed
OL,4,Cfor attempted murder
OL,6,FA paramedic who attended the scene
OL,7,Fsaid she could feel radiating heat
OL,8,Ffrom the hot oil on the floor.
OL,10,FMollah pleaded guilty to causing
OL,11,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent but
OL,12,Fdenied attempting to murder his wife.
OL,14,FA jury convicted him after a trial at
OL,15,FBirmingham Crown Court in August last
OL,16,Fyear and he was sentenced to 26 years
OL,17,Fin prison today.
OL,19,FAn indefinite restraining order was
OL,20,Falso imposed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
