FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777054266
OL,3,CMan who poured hot oil on wife jailed
OL,4,Cfor attempted murder
OL,6,FOn the day of the attack, Mollah came
OL,7,Fhome from work and told his wife to
OL,8,Fmake him an omelette, before he put
OL,9,Foil in a frying pan and waited for it
OL,10,Fto heat up.
OL,12,FWhen she turned away to wash a
OL,13,Futensil, Mollah grabbed her hair and
OL,14,Fpoured the hot oil over her face
OL,15,Fbefore hitting her repeatedly with the
OL,16,Fpan and a metal frame from the gas
OL,17,Fcooker.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
