OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777054266
OL,3,CMan who poured hot oil on wife jailed
OL,4,Cfor attempted murder
OL,6,FMollah suggested to police at the
OL,7,Fscene that his wife had fallen in an
OL,8,Faccident but when interviewed he
OL,9,Fclaimed he was defending himself.
OL,11,FTejinder Sandhu, a Senior Crown
OL,12,FProsecutor for CPS West Midlands,
OL,13,Fsaid: "This was a vicious and
OL,14,Fsustained attack that left the victim
OL,15,Fwith severe, life-changing injuries.
OL,17,F"Raju Mollah lied to minimise what he
OL,18,Fhad done by claiming self-defence but
OL,19,Fthe evidence proved he deliberately
OL,20,Fattacked his wife with the intention
OL,21,Fof killing her.
OL,26,@uD@GOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
