PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777054266
OL,3,CMan who poured hot oil on wife jailed
OL,4,Cfor attempted murder
OL,6,F"There is no excuse for such violence
OL,7,Fand we will continue to robustly
OL,8,Fprosecute those who commit such
OL,9,Fatrocious crimes as fully as the law
OL,10,Fallows."
